section_title: SBSTA IN-SESSION WORKSHOP ON IMPACTS OF, AND VULNERABILITY AND ADAPTATION TO, CLIMATE CHANGE
sentences: This in-session workshop was chaired by SBSTA Chair Benrageb.
Delegates heard presentations by experts, interspersed with question-and-answer discussions, and concluded with a wrap-up session.
enb_long_title: Tenth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
